I am kinda disapointed in our DD upgrade, sure it is nice we got a 1000pt DD firebased conjure spell, but it is not really an upgrade in dmg. It would have been nice if they acctually could have let us get an upgrade to match druids, now we really are the 3th best nukers and not just shared second.<P>It would also been nice if Quick summoning really means quick Conjuring....  If thats so quick summon would maybe be our most important skill.<P>I also slightly anoyed about our manaregen, the 3pt from the armor is good I guess, but more or less all classes get manaregen, clerics get self only for 6pt. Sure we can add an  other 4pt with waterform, but that requires 25skill points, and thats about the same required to get from L50 to L60 in exp. It also unknow how this manaregen will stack with Clarity/Potg/Shield/Flowing Thought/Bard song. Then also add the fact that it will make you kos to more mobs, while this no biggie in most raids (since you kos to start with) it is a big deal in some places.<P>I also kinda anoyed with the summon armor spells, I really think they going to be useless, atleast at high levels, noone really want a 17ac BP, maybe for cr but thats it. If it helps pet .. then it can be usefull. On the other hand all classes got lower level spells that is useless at high levels, so no biggie if they chose armor summonings as our useless spells.<BR>The other thing that bothers me is the wasted new AC buff, while better than phantom armor, it get outdated at L58 (if they don't stack .. doubt that...).<BR>The pet heals also to low, should been 1-3 ratio atleast. <P>So basicly on the spell side I think we got shafted bigtime compared to other classes.<BR>On the otherside, if pets nukes got better and we the only one getting /pet hold, we might improve on that part alot.
